title: RuntimeError: Error(s) in loading state_dict for Tacotron
body:
I'm trying to generate speech from the latest checkpoint. I did

- Checkout this project
- Download "Tacotron2-iter-260K" checkpoint "checkpoint_261000.pth.tar" and "config.json" from  table https://github.com/mozilla/TTS#checkpoints-and-audio-samples
- Checkout git commit "824c091" from same table
- Install with `python setup.py develop`
- Modify "server/conf.json" to point on the two files from step 1
- Start the server with `python server/server.py -c server/conf.json`

I get the following error

```bash
AttributeError: 'AttrDict' object has no attribute 'embedding_size'
```

Which is easy to fix with `embedding_size: "256"`, then I get:
